UUTrack.Controller.devices.PhotonicScience.scmoscam module¶

“scmoscam” is a wrapper class originally written by Perceval Guillou, perceval@photonic-science.com in Py2 and has been tested successfully with scmoscontrol.dll SCMOS Pleora (GEV) control dll (x86 )v5.6.0.0 (date modified 10/2/2013)

SaFa @nanoLINX has adapted the wrapper class for a camera control program.

v1.0, 24 feb. 2015, @author: SaFa {S.Faez@uu.nl}
